    "created_at": "2015-06-12T09:14:15Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-06-12T09:14:15Z",
    "body": "There is nothing unsafe about looping forever, so I strongly oppose a `panic!()`. As a user I would expect `(a..b).step_by(c).take(n)` to work for all `c`, without having to special case for `c == 0`..\n",
