    "updated_at": "2015-06-12T16:52:43Z",
    "body": "This is currently intended behavior, and for now I'm going to close this in favor of the [discussion in stabilizing `step_by`](https://internals.rust-lang.org/t/step-by-on-negative-numbers/2231/6) as this is definitely a useful data point, but perhaps not big enough to have its own issue right now.\n",
